    "learning_outcomes": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "for the degree of Bachelor of Science in Liberal Arts & Sciences Major in Astronomy plus Data Science"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "The Astronomy + Data Science program has learning objectives in both Astronomy and Data Science."
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": "h2",
        "content": "The Astronomy learning objectives are:"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "list_type": "ol",
        "content": [
          "Understand the hierarchical architecture of the cosmos, increasing in scale from the Solar System to the Galaxy to the Universe, and decreasing in scale to atoms and their nuclei. Understand the interplay among these scales.",
          "Define and use fundamental principles and techniques of astronomy and astrophysics.\n\t\nIdentify which principles should be applied to a specified situation.\nShow familiarity with astronomical observables and their physical origin.\nUnderstand and apply basic physics and computational techniques to solve problems in astronomy, and interpret the results.",
          "Analyze astronomical data, and quantitative data generally.\n\t\nDemonstrate the ability to link observation and theory.\nDemonstrate the ability to draw qualitative conclusions from quantitative information, and vice versa.\nDemonstrate the ability to plan observational programs, use astronomical telescopes and instrumentation, and to analyze and present astronomical data.",
          "Plan and perform guided research, or attain an advanced-level understanding of a topic of contemporary interest in astronomy.",
          "Demonstrate the ability to communicate effectively both verbally and in writing."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": "h2",
        "content": "The Data Science learning objectives are:"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "list_type": "ol",
        "content": [
          "Demonstrate proficiency with statistical and computational analysis of data.",
          "Create informative and accurate visualizations of data.",
          "Build and evaluate data-based models.",
          "Describe, curate, and manage data.",
          "Understand and manage issues of reproducibility in data science.",
          "Understand and address ethical issues in data science such as access, bias, and privacy.",
          "Apply data science skills and concepts in projects or research, and communicate and interpret the results of data analysis."
        ]
      }
    ],
